Refined Prompt:

Role:
You are an expert logo designer specializing in luxury fashion branding.
Objective:
Create a logo for a fashion brand that manufactures garments, reflecting sophistication, heritage, and modern refinement.
Background:
The brand is an old, established fashion house that is currently undergoing a restructuring, transitioning from its legacy identity into a more contemporary visual presence while retaining its sense of heritage and craftsmanship.
Target Audience:
Luxury-class consumers who value understated elegance, quality craftsmanship, and timeless design over bold or trend-driven aesthetics.
Requirements:

Use only subtle, muted, and sophisticated colors (e.g., ivory, beige, muted charcoal, dusty taupe, deep muted navy) — no bright, saturated, or high-contrast tones
Logo mark must be an abstract, textile-inspired symbol (evoking a fabric fold, drape, weave, or stitch line) in clean geometric strokes — not a literal illustration
Typography: refined serif or slim modern sans-serif, uppercase, wide letter spacing (placeholder brand name: "MAISON NOIRE")
Must include a tagline placed directly below the main wordmark, in a smaller, lighter-weight font, with clear visual hierarchy (placeholder tagline: "Est. [Year] — Tailored Heritage")
Composition should be centered and symmetrical: abstract symbol on top, wordmark below, tagline beneath that
Background: solid white or transparent, flat vector style — no gradients, drop shadows, or photorealistic textures

Constraints:

No animal imagery of any kind
Only subtle/muted colors — no bright, neon, or high-contrast palettes
No intricate or overly detailed elements that would be lost at small scale

Output Format:
Generate a detailed logo design (or image generation prompt) following the above template — deliverable as a clean, isolated vector-style design, provided in formats suitable for embroidery, print, storefront signage, app icons, and digital/social media use (square and horizontal-lockup versions).
Evaluation Criteria:

Design must be entirely original and must not copy, replicate, or closely resemble any existing brand logo
Final image/design must be usable and legible across all platforms and sizes — from small tags to large signage — without loss of clarity


